<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <style>
    .contact-item {
      border: 1px solid var(--zinc-800);
      background: rgba(24,24,27,0.7); /* Increased opacity for better contrast */
      color: var(--white); /* Changed text color to white for better readability */
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s, background-color 0.2s;
    }
    .contact-item:hover {
      border-color: rgba(124,58,237,0.6); /* Slightly brighter border on hover */
      background: rgba(124,58,237,0.2); /* Subtle background change on hover */
      color: var(--zinc-900); /* Darker text color on hover */
    }
  </style>
</head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Proximamente Imaf | Mecanizados y Utillaje CLM</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Imaf S.L. — Mecanizado CNC y utillaje industrial en Talavera de la Reina. Nueva web en construcción." />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@700;900&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --orange: #7c3aed; /* Cambiado a morado */
      --zinc-950: #f9f9f9; /* Cambiado a un blanco no puro */
      --zinc-900: #18181b;
      --zinc-800: #27272a;
      --zinc-500: #71717a;
      --zinc-400: #a1a1aa;
      --white: #ffffff;
    }
    html, body { height: 100%; background: var(--zinc-950); color: var(--zinc-900); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; overflow: hidden; }
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: linear-gradient(var(--zinc-800) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, var(--zinc-800) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
      opacity: 0.3;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      top: -20%;
      right: -10%;
      width: 600px;
      height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,58,237,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%); /* Actualizado a morado */
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .container { position: relative; z-index: 10; height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; }
    .bracket { position: fixed; width: 32px; height: 32px; }
    .bracket--tl { top: 2rem; left: 2rem; border-top: 2px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.7); border-left: 2px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.7); }
    .bracket--tr { top: 2rem; right: 2rem; border-top: 2px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.7); border-right: 2px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.7); }
    .bracket--bl { bottom: 2rem; left: 2rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.7); border-left: 2px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.7); }
    .bracket--br { bottom: 2rem; right: 2rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.7); border-right: 2px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.7); }
    .line-left { position: fixed; left: 0; top: 20%; width: 1px; height: 60%; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(124,58,237,0.5), transparent); }
    .line-right { position: fixed; right: 0; top: 30%; width: 1px; height: 40%; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(113,113,122,0.3), transparent); }
    .label { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards; opacity: 0; }
    .label-line { width: 24px; height: 1px; background: var(--orange); }
    .label-text { color: var(--orange); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.1s forwards; opacity: 0; }
    .logo-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; background: var(--orange); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .logo-icon span { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #000; }
    .logo-name { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.75rem; color: var(--zinc-900); line-height: 1; }
    .logo-sub { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--zinc-500); margin-top: 2px; }
    h1 { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem); line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.2s forwards; opacity: 0; }
    h1 span { color: var(--orange); }
    p { color: var(--zinc-400); font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 480px; margin-bottom: 3rem; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.3s forwards; opacity: 0; }
    .contact { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.4s forwards; opacity: 0; }
    .contact-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid var(--zinc-800); background: rgba(24,24,27,0.5); padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; color: var(--zinc-400); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.875rem; transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s; }
    .contact-item:hover { border-color: rgba(124,58,237,0.4); color: var(--zinc-900); }
    .contact-item svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; color: var(--orange); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .progress-wrap { position: fixed; bottom: 3rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: min(400px, calc(100vw - 4rem)); animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.5s forwards; opacity: 0; }
    .progress-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--zinc-500); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .progress-bar { height: 2px; background: var(--zinc-800); width: 100%; }
    .progress-fill { height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--orange), rgba(124,58,237,0.4)); width: 0%; animation: fillBar 2s ease 1s forwards; }
    @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    @keyframes fillBar { to { width: 65%; } }
    @media (max-width: 480px) { .bracket { display: none; } .contact { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bracket bracket--tl"></div>
  <div class="bracket bracket--tr"></div>
  <div class="bracket bracket--bl"></div>
  <div class="bracket bracket--br"></div>
  <div class="line-left"></div>
  <div class="line-right"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">
      <div class="label-line"></div>
      <span class="label-text">Talavera de la Reina · CLM</span>
      <div class="label-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="logo">
      <div class="logo-icon"><span>I</span></div>
      <div class="logo-text">
        <div class="logo-name">IMAF</div>
        <div class="logo-sub">Mecanizados y Utillaje CLM</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h1>Nueva web<br /><span>en construcción</span></h1>
    <p>Estamos trabajando en algo mejor. Mientras tanto puedes contactarnos directamente — seguimos fabricando a pleno rendimiento.</p>
    <div class="contact">
      <a href="tel:+34925800695" class="contact-item">
        <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
        +34 925 80 06 95
      </a>
      <a href="mailto:info@maquimaf.es" class="contact-item">
        <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
        josemaria@maquimaf.es
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="progress-wrap">
    <div class="progress-label">
      <span>Desarrollo en progreso</span>
      <span>50%</span>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-bar">
      <div class="progress-fill"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>